image_analysis.description: A photograph of an interior corner with wood-paneled walls. On the wall hangs a framed black and white portrait of Albert Einstein. Below the portrait is a small wooden side table or nightstand. On the table sits a glass candle holder and a stack of three books. To the right, the edge of another framed picture with an ornate gold frame is visible. To the left is a wooden door frame.
image_analysis.layout: Interior scene showing a corner of a room with furniture and wall art.
